rows.label: tev062001_MSG0001
rows.name:
Yoyotsu is on quest to eat every last yummy food
on Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062001_MSG0002
rows.name:
Latest and greatest thing Yoyotsu try is scrumptious
food called "evello."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062001_MSG0003
rows.name:
Dangly thing in throat of evello smell delicious.
Also taste totally crunchy when grilled.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062001_MSG0004
rows.name:
Is this what friends call...delicacy?
And can Yoyotsu sell it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062001_MSG0008
rows.name: Mamapon goes out and hunts food we eat.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062001_MSG0009
rows.name:
If it looks edible, chances are Mamapon has bagged it
at least once.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062001_MSG0010
rows.name:
Mamapon says her next hunting trip will be to Twisty
Turny Tree! Humans call it Coil Tree Cape.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062001_MSG0011
rows.name:
Hmm, does that mean fish? Yoyotsu want to eat fish!
Yum![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062001_MSG0016
rows.name:
Yoyotsu forgot to pack lunch when going to look
for Satsu. Meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062001_MSG0017
rows.name:
So Yoyotsu ate raw kusakiri stag beetles and grilled
morphling flounders instead.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062001_MSG0018
rows.name: Mumutsu said Yoyotsu could survive anywhere![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062001_MSG0019
rows.name:
Is that major compliment? Is this birth of wilderness
survivor Yoyotsu?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062001_MSG0025
rows.name:
Yoyotsu is on quest to eat every last yummy food
on Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062001_MSG0026
rows.name:
Latest and greatest thing Yoyotsu try is scrumptious
food called "lophid liver."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062001_MSG0027
rows.name: [ST:playername ] can try it too! So easy![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062001_MSG0028
rows.name:
Just defeat lophid, then rip open belly and tear out
gooey, delicious liver.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev062001_MSG0029
rows.name:
Watching liver quiver will make friend shiver!
It is true Miran delicacy.[ST:wait ]
